snippet.title: Spyragon: Jackpot Matches
snippet.description:
Spyragon is available to play on the iOS App Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/spyragon/id1584715775

In Spyragon Classic, the ultimate goal is to create Stars, Combos, or Full Hexagons.  But when you create many of those in the same move, you have really hit the jackpot!

Directions available at: https://spyraverse.com

Also follow us on Facebook, Instagram, and Twitter: @spyraverse
